## How to Use

### Generate a component from scratch:
1. Select `figma-to-aem` chat mode
2. Paste your Figma URL
3. Copilot generates all 5 files

### Generate a component manually:
1. Select `htl-developer` mode → get HTL
2. Switch to `dialog-builder` mode → get dialog XML
3. Switch to `sass-developer` mode → get SASS
4. Switch to `js-developer` mode → get JS
5. Switch to `test-writer` mode → get tests

### Review code:
1. Select the files to review
2. Switch to `code-reviewer` mode
3. Type "Review this component"

### Run E2E tests:
1. Ensure AEM is running on localhost:4502/4503
2. Playwright MCP can automate browser testing directly from chat
